#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn4.15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.15:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. Rule "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn4.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Mānasasutta "
msgstr "15. A Mental Snare "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn4.15:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "sn4.15:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.15:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked went up to the Buddha and addressed him in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.249, sc2
msgctxt "sn4.15:2.1"
msgid "“Antalikkhacaro pāso, "
msgstr "“There’s a mental snare "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.15:2.2"
msgid "yvāyaṃ carati mānaso; "
msgstr "wandering the sky. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.15:2.3"
msgid "Tena taṃ bādhayissāmi, "
msgstr "I’ll bind you with it—"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.15:2.4"
msgid "na me samaṇa mokkhasī”ti. "
msgstr "you won’t escape me, ascetic!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn4.15:3.1"
msgid "“Rūpā saddā rasā gandhā, "
msgstr "“Sights, sounds, tastes, smells, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.15:3.2"
msgid "Phoṭṭhabbā ca manoramā; "
msgstr "and touches so delightful: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.15:3.3"
msgid "Ettha me vigato chando, "
msgstr "desire for these is gone from me. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.15:3.4"
msgid "Nihato tvamasi antakā”ti. "
msgstr "You’re beaten, terminator!” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn4.15:4.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ bhagavā, jānāti maṃ sugato”ti dukkhī dummano tatthevantaradhāyīti. "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The Buddha knows me! The Holy One knows me!” miserable and sad, vanished right there."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
